caption:
Double trouble and mutant magic — BossKong style.
These sketch covers don’t just pop—they punch!!

Front to back, it’s all attitude, color, and chaos.
From Harley & Ivy to Magik & Colossus, the squad is stacked and the vibes are savage.

Original art. Unfiltered energy.
Only the bold wear the BossKong crown.
